Congratulations to the 56 #GoProAward recipients taking home $17,857 each. 🤑

node.text:
Life is different this year—but adversity invites us to reconnect with what matters most. Separated by 24 countries, 60 #GoProAthletes #GoProFamily members were challenged to dream up + take their own fulfilling adventures. For four days, the group dropped everything to find beauty in their backyards. Whether it was a hike with the family, a strike-mission for a swell, or tank of gas without a destination, it was captured on #GoProHERO9 Black + saved forever. 🤙
